(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Integration in Mathematics using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind anti-derivatives and area ideas.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Integration to examples such as integrating a simple polynomial expression.) Tj
T*
